        <IsA>service</IsA>
        <Summary>Repeater controller and EchoLink (simplex or repeater)</Summary>
        <Description>The SvxLink project is a multi purpose voice services system for ham radio use. For example, EchoLink connections are supported. Also, the SvxLink server can act as a repeater controller.</Description>
